---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="A bit about Johnathan Neals."
	pubDate={new Date()}
>
	<p>
		I'm Johnathan Neals. I work on systems where reliability matters — the part of engineering
		where you measure success in fewer surprises, not more features.
	</p>

	<p>
		Right now I'm building a multi-agent platform on top of a shared persistent memory substrate.
		Most of what shows up here will be lessons I extract from that work: drift detection,
		operational discipline, how to design for honest failure modes, what to do when an LLM tries
		to convince you of something that isn't true.
	</p>

	<p>
		If something here resonates or you want to follow up, the easiest way to reach me is via
		<a href="https://github.com/johnathanneals-dev">GitHub</a>.
	</p>
</Layout>
